Kontakt,io,is,a,beacon,hardware,and,software,platform,The,Kontakt,io,API,allows,developers,to,get,information,on,and,update,their,beacon,devices,Beacons,are,small,Bluetooth,radio,transmitters,that,broadcast,a,signal,at,regular,intervals,Bluetooth,equipped,devices,like,smartphones,can,detect,beacons,once,they,re,in,range,The,combination,of,the,Kontakt,io,API,and,the,Kontakt,io,beacons,allow,developers,to,create,proximity,based,solutions